# Readme

## Purpose:

1. To build a dashboard exploring trending in Philadelphia 311 calls.
2. To showcase [Shiny](https://shiny.posit.co/) as a tool for dashboard development, and to practice with it.
3. To showcase [Targets](https://books.ropensci.org/targets/) 
4. To showcase text analysis using topic modeling with [STM](https://cran.r-project.org/web/packages/stm/vignettes/stmVignette.pdf).

### How do we get the data?

- All data is pulled by API call from the 311 OpenDataPhilly endpoint.  [For details, see their page](https://opendataphilly.org/datasets/311-service-and-information-requests/)



